  <thing id="imodRunicThunder" name="Runic Thunder" description="When its weapon strikes a foe, this rune carving flashes white like a bolt of lightning. The deafening boom of thunder comes a half-second later, staggering the foe with concussive force.\n\n{b}Use With:{/b} This attachment can be applied to any weapon.\n\n{b}Modifiers:{/b} The weapon gains the Concussive 1 item quality.\n\n{b}Hard Points Required:{/b} 2." compset="ItemMod">
