  <thing id="wpMagicStaff" name="Magic Staff" description="Most of the mages in Terrinoth prefer the trusty and reliable staff over other options. Whether carved from wood, forged from iron, or even wrought from bone, a staff signifies travel and distance. This link helps wizards increase the range at which they can cast spells. A staff also doubles as a handy walking stick for many an elderly mage on the road.\n\nWhen your character casts a spell while using a magic staff, the first Range effect added to the spell does not increase the spell’s difficulty. In addition, Attack spells cast by your character increase their base damage by four." compset="Melee" summary="When casting a spell while using a magic staff, the first Range effect added to the spell does not increase the spell’s difficulty. Also, Attack spells increase base damage by four.">
